## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/macho/dyld-chained-starts-in-image">dyld&#95;chained&#95;starts&#95;in&#95;image</a> is embedded in LC&#95;DYLD&#95;CHAINED&#95;FIXUPS payload.

Each seg&#95;info&#95;offset entry is the offset into this struct for that segment followed by pool of dyld&#95;chain&#95;starts&#95;in&#95;segment data.
